Employer.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style=""><span style="font-size: 14.6667px;">Type of employee contract: {CONTRACT_TYPE}.</span></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">III. EMPLOYMENT PERIOD</span></b><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">. The Employer agrees
