modified or amended under the condition that any such amendment is attached and
authorized by all parties. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">XXI. SEVERABILITY</span></b><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">. This Agreement shall
remain in effect in the event a section or provision is unenforceable or
invalid. All remaining sections and provisions shall be deemed legally binding
unless a court rules that any such provision or section is invalid or
unenforceable, thus, limiting the effect of another provision or section. In
such case, the affected provision or section shall be enforced as so limited.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">XXII. WAIVER OF
CONTRACTUAL RIGHT</span></b><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:" arial",sans-serif"="">S.
